&ldquo;Sorry &hellip; I cannot join the standup, because I was not able to find a WLAN hotspot.&rdquo; &ldquo;Can you hear me? Sorry &hellip; I am on a shitty/weak WLAN.&rdquo; &ldquo;Sorry &hellip; can we switch off the video.

